# Keep the generated printer database and its generator checked out with LF on
# every OS. Windows CI otherwise converts them to CRLF, and the byte-for-byte
# `npm run validate:printers` check (and clean diffs on regeneration) depend on
# a stable line ending.
src/data/printers.json text eol=lf
scripts/generate-printer-database.mjs text eol=lf
